Go to the junkyard and find an OEM Honda stereo. Decent sound and prob about $20 or less. 

I put one on my motorcycle to replace the analog stereo - took too long to change channels and thus was a safety hazard. The digital honda stereo was GREAT! I have a second one on hand for my next swap. 

